latestPosts.caption:
Get the perfect fit for your MWK Press-On Nails with these easy measuring tips! ✨

1️⃣ Use a flexible measuring tape, a strip of paper, or even scotch tape to measure the width of each nail.
2️⃣ Measure directly using a ruler for quick and precise results.
3️⃣ If your thumb is a small size, all your fingers are likely small too, so you can go for size S! Same rule applies for Medium and Large. If you’re unsure, it’s best to measure all your fingers to ensure a perfect fit💅

Follow these steps to ensure your MWK Press-On Nails look flawless and feel comfortable. Ready to glam up your nails? Head over to our website and get your perfect set today!

latestPosts.caption:
Every Jainsem I’ve ever worn has been my mom’s.
I don’t own one myself🙈I hardly wear them.
My Mom wore this in her early 40s, probably once or twice.

While she was draping this on me, in that quiet moment, with her hands adjusting every fold, it didn’t feel like I was just borrowing a piece of clothing…
I was borrowing a memory, a moment, a little bit of her grace.

#GRWM #NaraJainsem #MomAndMe #KhasiTradition #HeirloomStyle #BorrowedBeauty #KhasiCulture #SlowFashion #LegacyInFabric
